        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">Living in Dallas...I just got back from the attending the Fan Faire.  Here are some pertinent notes...</P><P>Spell Forum--Poe</P><P>DoT stacking Issue<BR>Poe agreed that DoT's should stack so two characters could be able to cast the same spell on a mob.  He said the problem is in the difficulty of coding this.</P><P>All Kunark spells have the same chance to drop.  No spell is made to drop more often than another.  Drop tables for the spells are the same.</P><P>Will look into allowing translocate without gouping.</P><P>Skills are capped at 252.  Items can get you up to this cap...if your class cap is lower. (in the developer's forum, I thought they said caps were 255)</P><P>Someone asked about being able to see your buff by holding the control key...much like the use of seeing spell names by holding the alt key.</P><P>And finally...the answer you have been pondering...Flowing Thought points are capped at 15.  So, the max increase in manna per tick from FT items in 15.</P><P>The Developers Forum was full of the stuff you would expect.  Nothing new except that the new interface will have 8 spells per spell book page AND they will look into allowing you to mem a full page of spells at a time.</P><P>Ishtarra Gemeinseele<BR>Warlock of the Dirty Soul<BR>Uber N00b Extraordinaire<BR>Tunare Server</P><P>Edited by - ishtarra on 01/28/2002  09:32:32</font></td>
